creator: Bluecarsharing SAS
descriptionHtml:
BlueSG is the First Large-Scale Electric Vehicle car-sharing service in Singapore

Our primary goal is to offer simple, affordable and easy access to our electric vehicles and charging stations in Singapore. Our fleet of 100% electric vehicles is available 24/7 to facilitate your life and your daily transport around Singapore.

Try out our official App to :
- Reserve a vehicle and a parking spot
- Search for the closest stations around you and your destination
- Check out all your account history directly in the app
